        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JVC for corrections in <hi rend="italic">Insectivorous plants</hi>. Explains confusion of fluid and dry measures. The work has sold well in England.</p>  
<p>Repeats suggestion that JVC employ someone to translate <hi rend="italic">Climbing plants</hi> under his supervision.</p> 
